## Description {#details}

An Iterator adapter using an InnerInvGraphT::iterator as a base iterator, and storing the <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/xray/graph/#aa7d4f1e9198ebd47ab0fc3cef797ac86">VertexIdentifier</a> the iterator range comes from.

The dereference operator is then performed using a pointer to the graph&#39;s edge set.

Definition at line 131 of file <a href="/docs/api/files/include/include/llvm/include/llvm/xray/graph-h">Graph.h</a>.
